1
00:00:25,280 --> 00:00:27,480
We've been wandering around here
for so many days.

2
00:00:27,480 --> 00:00:28,940
Have you found that Zhang—

3
00:00:29,120 --> 00:00:30,380
what's his name again?

4
00:00:30,870 --> 00:00:32,030
Have you found him?

5
00:00:33,110 --> 00:00:33,960
Southeast,

6
00:00:34,640 --> 00:00:35,640
southwest,

7
00:00:37,100 --> 00:00:37,920
east market,

8
00:00:38,640 --> 00:00:39,570
and west market.

9
00:00:39,920 --> 00:00:42,200
Six central ministries, and 32 blocks.

10
00:00:43,030 --> 00:00:44,590
We are here to find someone,

11
00:00:44,920 --> 00:00:46,730
not to study the map of Tangjing.

12
00:00:47,200 --> 00:00:48,330
Come and take a look.

13
00:00:48,360 --> 00:00:49,490
Where is this place?

14
00:00:56,030 --> 00:00:56,630
This

15
00:00:57,470 --> 00:01:00,070
is the former site
of Qingluan Altar in Tangjing.

16
00:01:00,070 --> 00:01:01,960
It is bordered by the Capital Prefecture
to the left

17
00:01:01,960 --> 00:01:03,840
and the Empress's Furong Garden
to the right.

18
00:01:03,840 --> 00:01:05,310
Nominally it has been abandoned
for a long time

19
00:01:05,310 --> 00:01:07,190
and isn't even drawn on the map.

20
00:01:07,790 --> 00:01:10,230
However, it is surrounded
by three watchtowers,

21
00:01:10,230 --> 00:01:12,789
which are guarded day and night.

22
00:01:15,870 --> 00:01:18,100
This is the secret residence of Director Zhang
that we are looking for.

23
00:01:18,100 --> 00:01:19,230
We will act tonight.

24
00:02:41,450 --> 00:02:46,380
[REBIRTH]

25
00:02:46,910 --> 00:02:49,350
[Episode 12]

26
00:02:50,960 --> 00:02:52,370
[Virtue of Zhang's Mansion]

27
00:03:28,079 --> 00:03:29,430
I've searched the east wings.

28
00:03:29,430 --> 00:03:30,350
No one was there.

29
00:03:30,350 --> 00:03:31,680
He's not here. Let's go.

30
00:03:46,860 --> 00:03:48,030
There are traps everywhere.

31
00:03:48,030 --> 00:03:48,660
Let's go.

32
00:03:52,270 --> 00:03:53,150
You're injured?

33
00:03:53,150 --> 00:03:53,910
Who's there?

34
00:03:55,730 --> 00:03:57,190
Go! I'll go lead them away!

35
00:04:03,690 --> 00:04:04,430
The intruders are over there!

36
00:04:04,430 --> 00:04:05,080
After them!

37
00:04:05,080 --> 00:04:05,560
Yes!

38
00:04:10,300 --> 00:04:11,560
The intruders are just ahead!

39
00:04:11,560 --> 00:04:12,280
After them!

40
00:04:27,380 --> 00:04:27,990
Search!

41
00:04:45,920 --> 00:04:46,650
Who's there?

42
00:04:52,120 --> 00:04:53,650
Greetings, Your Highness.

43
00:04:53,870 --> 00:04:55,530
The people you're looking for

44
00:04:55,950 --> 00:04:56,870
went that way.

45
00:04:57,110 --> 00:04:57,670
Yes.

46
00:04:57,850 --> 00:04:58,510
Let's go!

47
00:05:05,360 --> 00:05:06,000
Xing?

48
00:05:17,310 --> 00:05:17,950
Xing,

49
00:05:18,710 --> 00:05:20,440
I know you have many questions,

50
00:05:20,920 --> 00:05:23,070
and I should give you some explanation.

51
00:05:23,070 --> 00:05:24,600
But I have my reasons not to.

52
00:05:25,560 --> 00:05:26,360
Zhuge Yue,

53
00:05:27,510 --> 00:05:29,910
I know you've been protecting me silently.

54
00:05:30,310 --> 00:05:31,480
If it weren't for me,

55
00:05:32,040 --> 00:05:34,770
you wouldn't have nearly died
in the frozen lake.

56
00:05:35,600 --> 00:05:37,680
Xing, it was not your fault.

57
00:05:37,870 --> 00:05:38,800
I...

58
00:05:40,270 --> 00:05:42,400
I thought we had a tacit understanding

59
00:05:42,600 --> 00:05:44,000
and knew each other well.

60
00:05:44,480 --> 00:05:46,600
We even went through
life and death together.

61
00:05:46,600 --> 00:05:47,720
What exactly is it

62
00:05:47,720 --> 00:05:49,680
that we can't face together?

63
00:05:52,820 --> 00:05:55,430
I didn't expect you to still refuse
to tell me.

64
00:05:56,750 --> 00:05:58,360
I could only help you this much today.

65
00:05:58,360 --> 00:05:59,360
From now on,

66
00:06:00,160 --> 00:06:01,240
I will tell myself

67
00:06:01,630 --> 00:06:03,510
that the old Zhuge Yue sank into

68
00:06:04,510 --> 00:06:07,170
the frozen lake forever
while trying to save me.

69
00:06:14,940 --> 00:06:16,010
I'm sorry, Xing.

70
00:06:17,060 --> 00:06:19,460
If I could still stand before you
properly,

71
00:06:20,040 --> 00:06:22,300
I would definitely tell you everything.

72
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:48,430
The audience has arrived.
Let the show begin!

73
00:06:49,170 --> 00:06:51,170
Today we will present you

74
00:06:51,390 --> 00:06:54,870
"General Chu's Three Attacks
on Zhuge Yue".

75
00:06:55,540 --> 00:06:57,300
The plot has ups and downs

76
00:06:57,680 --> 00:06:59,140
and is deeply satisfying!

77
00:06:59,240 --> 00:07:01,390
It's truly an excellent script.

78
00:07:01,710 --> 00:07:02,270
Li Ce,

79
00:07:02,720 --> 00:07:03,800
you're so lame.

80
00:07:05,600 --> 00:07:06,510
Whether it's lame or not,

81
00:07:06,510 --> 00:07:08,770
you have to watch it before you can judge.

82
00:07:09,800 --> 00:07:10,800
The first strike

83
00:07:11,480 --> 00:07:13,750
is for his eternally cold face.

84
00:07:14,190 --> 00:07:15,040
He has a mouth,

85
00:07:15,190 --> 00:07:16,360
but he never uses it properly.

86
00:07:16,360 --> 00:07:17,830
Keeping a straight face all day,

87
00:07:17,830 --> 00:07:19,720
as if the whole world owes him.

88
00:07:24,950 --> 00:07:25,480
Qiao,

89
00:07:25,870 --> 00:07:27,800
do you think that was a good strike?

90
00:07:29,510 --> 00:07:30,310
Wait a minute.

91
00:07:30,600 --> 00:07:32,000
There's a second strike.

92
00:07:32,360 --> 00:07:33,420
This second strike

93
00:07:33,480 --> 00:07:35,270
is for his arrogance

94
00:07:35,270 --> 00:07:36,270
and superiority.

95
00:07:36,390 --> 00:07:38,830
He's just an ordinary person
made of flesh and blood,

96
00:07:38,830 --> 00:07:40,870
but he has to act like an immortal
descended to earth,

97
00:07:40,870 --> 00:07:42,630
capable of handling all problems.

98
00:07:42,630 --> 00:07:43,490
And the result?

99
00:07:48,430 --> 00:07:50,240
He ended up covered in scars,

100
00:07:50,390 --> 00:07:52,320
which made others feel bad for him.

101
00:08:00,750 --> 00:08:01,960
The third strike

102
00:08:03,120 --> 00:08:05,510
is for Zhuge Yue's self-righteousness.

103
00:08:06,270 --> 00:08:07,750
He always claims

104
00:08:07,800 --> 00:08:09,080
that everything he does

105
00:08:09,080 --> 00:08:10,710
is to protect Qiao.

106
00:08:11,390 --> 00:08:12,570
Without consulting anyone,

107
00:08:12,570 --> 00:08:13,780
he has done many dangerous things

108
00:08:13,780 --> 00:08:15,240
in the name of protection.

109
00:08:15,680 --> 00:08:17,370
Does Qiao need your protection?

110
00:08:17,370 --> 00:08:20,250
Qiao is the world-renowned General Chu.

111
00:08:20,720 --> 00:08:22,830
She can protect herself.

112
00:08:33,720 --> 00:08:34,650
How was it, Qiao?

113
00:08:35,360 --> 00:08:36,490
Do you like the play?

114
00:08:36,799 --> 00:08:37,830
If you do,

115
00:08:37,870 --> 00:08:39,130
I've prepared Act Two.

116
00:08:40,240 --> 00:08:43,320
"General Chu Meets
the Crown Prince of Biantang By Chance,

117
00:08:43,320 --> 00:08:46,140
Fake Drama Turns Into Real Fate."

118
00:08:50,270 --> 00:08:50,960
Li Ce.

119
00:08:51,750 --> 00:08:52,950
I want to have a drink.

120
00:08:53,150 --> 00:08:53,840
Drink?

121
00:08:55,270 --> 00:08:55,950
Li Ce.

122
00:08:56,910 --> 00:08:57,790
Let me ask you.

123
00:08:59,000 --> 00:09:01,800
You said you liked Princess Fu
when you were young.

124
00:09:02,670 --> 00:09:04,240
But besides Princess Fu,

125
00:09:05,030 --> 00:09:07,670
you have so many female confidants
around you,

126
00:09:07,910 --> 00:09:10,600
and a large group
of beauties in your mansion.

127
00:09:11,120 --> 00:09:12,080
Are you sincere

128
00:09:13,750 --> 00:09:15,700
to all of them?

129
00:09:17,630 --> 00:09:18,910
Of course not.

130
00:09:20,390 --> 00:09:21,320
With some,

131
00:09:22,200 --> 00:09:24,320
I'm just playing along.

132
00:09:25,360 --> 00:09:26,270
With others,

133
00:09:27,200 --> 00:09:28,720
they are fair ladies.

134
00:09:29,150 --> 00:09:30,320
As a gentleman,

135
00:09:31,270 --> 00:09:32,550
I must woo them

136
00:09:33,550 --> 00:09:35,280
and take my time to admire them.

137
00:09:35,960 --> 00:09:37,200
It's like...

138
00:09:37,630 --> 00:09:40,200
appreciating a painting
or a piece of music.

139
00:09:41,150 --> 00:09:43,390
As for those I truly like,

140
00:09:50,120 --> 00:09:51,750
there are very, very few.

141
00:10:15,460 --> 00:10:16,770
I don't know why,

142
00:10:18,670 --> 00:10:20,290
but my feelings for him...

143
00:10:20,470 --> 00:10:22,610
are causing me pain.

144
00:10:23,750 --> 00:10:24,840
True love is to feel

145
00:10:26,960 --> 00:10:28,560
what the other person feels.

146
00:10:30,360 --> 00:10:32,030
You can sense his happiness,

147
00:10:32,520 --> 00:10:33,860
so naturally, you can also feel

148
00:10:33,860 --> 00:10:35,820
the pain and struggle in his heart.

149
00:10:36,440 --> 00:10:38,300
You would find joy because of him,

150
00:10:39,510 --> 00:10:42,570
and naturally,
you would also feel pain because of him.

151
00:10:48,840 --> 00:10:49,440
Li Ce,

152
00:10:51,390 --> 00:10:53,440
have you ever truly loved someone?

153
00:11:03,550 --> 00:11:04,950
It has already happened.

154
00:11:12,910 --> 00:11:13,510
Qiao.

155
00:11:40,010 --> 00:11:40,680
Li Ce!

156
00:11:45,150 --> 00:11:45,790
Qiao!

157
00:11:51,670 --> 00:11:52,840
Qiao!

158
00:12:54,290 --> 00:12:55,030
Here you go.

159
00:13:08,010 --> 00:13:08,650
Miss.

160
00:13:10,490 --> 00:13:11,550
What would you like to buy, miss?

161
00:13:11,550 --> 00:13:12,670
What did the lady

162
00:13:12,750 --> 00:13:14,440
just buy from you?

163
00:13:14,840 --> 00:13:16,320
She wasn't here to buy anything.

164
00:13:16,320 --> 00:13:18,720
She left that handkerchief here for sale.

165
00:13:18,870 --> 00:13:20,330
She is a regular customer.

166
00:13:20,510 --> 00:13:21,320
Selling a handkerchief?

167
00:13:21,320 --> 00:13:21,930
Yes.

168
00:13:22,240 --> 00:13:24,680
That lady embroiders a handkerchief
every month

169
00:13:24,680 --> 00:13:26,140
and brings it here to sell.

170
00:13:26,210 --> 00:13:26,750
And every time,

171
00:13:26,750 --> 00:13:28,240
it's sold

172
00:13:28,240 --> 00:13:29,320
within 1 hour.

173
00:13:29,510 --> 00:13:32,270
Do you know the person
who buys her handkerchiefs?

174
00:13:32,270 --> 00:13:33,800
Of course I don't know them.

175
00:13:34,200 --> 00:13:37,030
But it seems to always be the same lady,

176
00:13:37,200 --> 00:13:38,830
wearing a veil and a bamboo hat,

177
00:13:38,830 --> 00:13:40,120
wrapped up so tightly

178
00:13:40,400 --> 00:13:42,400
that her face can't be seen clearly.

179
00:13:43,880 --> 00:13:45,280
Is the handkerchief still here?

180
00:13:45,280 --> 00:13:46,040
Yes.

181
00:13:49,300 --> 00:13:50,960
I'll take this handkerchief.

182
00:13:51,320 --> 00:13:52,080
Here you go.

183
00:14:18,100 --> 00:14:19,300
Where is Wang Shi'er?

184
00:14:19,480 --> 00:14:20,910
He's slacking off
and not practicing again, right?

185
00:14:20,910 --> 00:14:22,150
Do you even need to ask?

186
00:14:22,150 --> 00:14:24,080
He's definitely upstairs, tinkering with

187
00:14:24,080 --> 00:14:25,880
his stupid contraptions again.

188
00:14:38,390 --> 00:14:39,150
Wang Shi'er!

189
00:14:45,370 --> 00:14:46,410
Wang Shi'er!

190
00:14:55,890 --> 00:14:58,130
Beautiful, you are so ruthless.

191
00:14:58,750 --> 00:14:59,960
I like it.

192
00:15:07,510 --> 00:15:08,200
Your Highness!

193
00:15:08,200 --> 00:15:09,360
Your Highness!

194
00:15:10,440 --> 00:15:12,680
Look at these new mechanisms I've set up.

195
00:15:12,680 --> 00:15:14,080
Aren't they pretty good?

196
00:15:14,880 --> 00:15:16,210
I was wrong! I was wrong!

197
00:15:16,560 --> 00:15:17,960
Take a look at this first.

198
00:15:21,910 --> 00:15:24,840
I feel there's something weird
about this handkerchief.

199
00:15:24,840 --> 00:15:25,790
The stitching is uneven,

200
00:15:25,790 --> 00:15:27,840
but it seems to follow a certain pattern.

201
00:15:27,840 --> 00:15:29,100
I can't be sure either.

202
00:15:30,360 --> 00:15:31,240
But I've seen something like this before

203
00:15:31,240 --> 00:15:33,360
in an ancient tomb in the southern border.

204
00:15:33,360 --> 00:15:34,510
Some tombs have symbols

205
00:15:34,510 --> 00:15:37,240
of varying lengths inscribed
to record secret messages.

206
00:15:37,240 --> 00:15:38,570
So you mean these stitches

207
00:15:38,570 --> 00:15:40,940
could be some sort of code?

208
00:15:45,420 --> 00:15:48,000
[Lyvwan Restaurant]

209
00:15:56,070 --> 00:15:58,310
Crown Prince, you're here.

210
00:15:59,870 --> 00:16:01,200
Lord Zhuge Ximeng,

211
00:16:01,910 --> 00:16:03,240
what do you want from me?

212
00:16:04,480 --> 00:16:05,390
I asked you here

213
00:16:06,110 --> 00:16:07,910
to discuss a collaboration with you.

214
00:16:07,910 --> 00:16:08,910
A collaboration?

215
00:16:09,000 --> 00:16:10,600
What kind of collaboration?

216
00:16:20,750 --> 00:16:22,080
I came to Biantang this time

217
00:16:22,080 --> 00:16:23,080
to find someone—

218
00:16:23,550 --> 00:16:25,240
Director Zhang Qingzhao
of the Ministry of Works.

219
00:16:25,240 --> 00:16:26,370
You help me find him,

220
00:16:26,630 --> 00:16:27,600
and I'll pay you.

221
00:16:27,670 --> 00:16:30,070
Director Zhang is a key confidential official
in the Ministry of Works.

222
00:16:30,070 --> 00:16:31,270
Why are you looking for him?

223
00:16:31,270 --> 00:16:33,840
I need a craft diagram he has.

224
00:16:34,270 --> 00:16:35,270
The techniques inside

225
00:16:35,270 --> 00:16:37,120
can help Ximeng mine black gold.

226
00:16:37,480 --> 00:16:38,960
If you're willing to cooperate with me,

227
00:16:38,960 --> 00:16:40,220
after the deal is done,

228
00:16:40,240 --> 00:16:42,360
you'll get 10 percent of the black gold

229
00:16:42,360 --> 00:16:43,200
from this mine.

230
00:16:43,200 --> 00:16:44,800
Ximeng has a black gold mine?

231
00:16:46,920 --> 00:16:49,590
But Director Zhang
is a pillar of Biantang.

232
00:16:50,130 --> 00:16:51,530
For nearly 40 years,

233
00:16:51,630 --> 00:16:53,820
he's been responsible
for all major casting

234
00:16:53,820 --> 00:16:55,560
and metallurgy tasks
in Biantang, including

235
00:16:55,560 --> 00:16:56,670
even military fortifications.

236
00:16:56,670 --> 00:16:58,390
What could
a mere title-holding Crown Prince like me

237
00:16:58,390 --> 00:16:59,360
possibly do to help you?

238
00:16:59,360 --> 00:17:00,390
You're right.

239
00:17:00,510 --> 00:17:02,440
You really can't help me with much.

240
00:17:02,720 --> 00:17:03,910
What do you mean by that?

241
00:17:03,910 --> 00:17:05,030
But first,

242
00:17:05,349 --> 00:17:06,510
currently, as the Crown Prince,

243
00:17:06,510 --> 00:17:07,920
you're responsible for my travels.

244
00:17:07,920 --> 00:17:09,270
You're like a sticky plaster

245
00:17:09,270 --> 00:17:10,400
I can't shake off.

246
00:17:10,690 --> 00:17:12,730
So it's better to be frank with you.

247
00:17:13,339 --> 00:17:14,869
I'm warning you, Zhuge Yue,

248
00:17:14,880 --> 00:17:16,349
if you keep talking like this,
we're done here.

249
00:17:16,349 --> 00:17:17,160
Second,

250
00:17:17,240 --> 00:17:19,000
although you have no power or influence,

251
00:17:19,000 --> 00:17:20,740
that's actually your strength.

252
00:17:20,740 --> 00:17:21,500
Strength?

253
00:17:21,880 --> 00:17:23,400
You are a puppet Crown Prince,

254
00:17:23,400 --> 00:17:25,109
so you need

255
00:17:25,109 --> 00:17:26,829
this 10 percent
of black gold more than anyone else.

256
00:17:26,829 --> 00:17:28,690
Are you saying I'm short of money?

257
00:17:28,920 --> 00:17:29,790
Who are you looking down on?

258
00:17:29,790 --> 00:17:31,850
You are the Crown Prince of Biantang.

259
00:17:32,070 --> 00:17:33,200
Without this 10 percent of the black gold,

260
00:17:33,200 --> 00:17:34,960
you naturally
won't lack food and clothing.

261
00:17:34,960 --> 00:17:36,220
But what if you have it?

262
00:17:37,070 --> 00:17:39,110
Perhaps you could turn the tables.

263
00:17:39,480 --> 00:17:40,350
You never know.

264
00:17:43,640 --> 00:17:45,310
But why should I cooperate with you?

265
00:17:45,310 --> 00:17:46,240
You are neither from Biantang,

266
00:17:46,240 --> 00:17:47,200
nor from Ximeng.

267
00:17:47,330 --> 00:17:48,730
Why should I believe you?

268
00:17:50,830 --> 00:17:53,070
But who else can you trust except me?

269
00:17:53,200 --> 00:17:54,720
Since you said
you only hold an empty title,

270
00:17:54,720 --> 00:17:55,880
I believe that in Biantang,

271
00:17:55,880 --> 00:17:57,830
you don't have many people you can trust.

272
00:17:57,830 --> 00:17:58,590
In that case,

273
00:17:58,590 --> 00:18:01,200
what does it matter whose side I'm on?

274
00:18:06,310 --> 00:18:07,000
Zhuge Yue,

275
00:18:07,330 --> 00:18:08,400
do you have a knife in your mouth?

276
00:18:08,400 --> 00:18:09,960
Why are you speaking so harshly?

277
00:18:09,960 --> 00:18:10,550
I just confessed my feelings

278
00:18:10,550 --> 00:18:12,450
to Qiao last night and got rejected.

279
00:18:12,450 --> 00:18:14,030
Now I'm pissed off because of you.

280
00:18:14,030 --> 00:18:15,630
What terrible luck do I have?

281
00:18:21,720 --> 00:18:22,510
Really?

282
00:18:23,310 --> 00:18:24,710
I didn't know about this.

283
00:18:25,110 --> 00:18:26,070
Sorry for what I said

284
00:18:26,070 --> 00:18:27,160
that upset you.

285
00:18:27,650 --> 00:18:28,890
I am truly sorry.

286
00:18:29,100 --> 00:18:29,960
How about this?

287
00:18:30,720 --> 00:18:31,780
As an apology,

288
00:18:33,070 --> 00:18:35,110
after this is done, I'll ask King Ximeng

289
00:18:35,110 --> 00:18:37,070
to give you an extra 10 percent
as compensation.

290
00:18:37,070 --> 00:18:38,070
What do you think?

291
00:18:40,720 --> 00:18:41,510
Zhuge Yue,

292
00:18:42,240 --> 00:18:42,960
come on!

293
00:18:42,960 --> 00:18:44,160
Please hide the smile on your face

294
00:18:44,160 --> 00:18:45,720
before you apologize to me, okay?

295
00:18:45,720 --> 00:18:46,440
Are you that happy

296
00:18:46,440 --> 00:18:47,970
that I was rejected by Qiao?

297
00:19:17,690 --> 00:19:25,100
[Chunxiao Theater]

298
00:19:56,360 --> 00:19:56,990
Take care.

299
00:20:01,180 --> 00:20:02,040
Your Highness,

300
00:20:02,400 --> 00:20:03,330
please come out.

301
00:20:09,590 --> 00:20:11,200
When did you notice me?

302
00:20:11,830 --> 00:20:12,920
During the day at the market,

303
00:20:12,920 --> 00:20:14,880
I saw you buy my handkerchief.

304
00:20:15,240 --> 00:20:16,590
On my way here just now,

305
00:20:17,000 --> 00:20:18,890
I sensed someone following me,

306
00:20:19,680 --> 00:20:21,000
so I guessed it was you.

307
00:20:21,240 --> 00:20:24,070
So you admit that the handkerchief

308
00:20:24,590 --> 00:20:26,510
is a tool for you
and the women in this theater

309
00:20:26,510 --> 00:20:27,790
to pass messages?

310
00:20:28,110 --> 00:20:28,680
Yes.

311
00:20:30,240 --> 00:20:32,040
It's hard for us to meet usually,

312
00:20:32,350 --> 00:20:35,010
so we've been using this method
to communicate.

313
00:20:39,720 --> 00:20:41,000
Who are you?

314
00:20:41,000 --> 00:20:42,590
You have already seen Rou.

315
00:20:42,830 --> 00:20:44,630
I can't hide it from you anymore.

316
00:20:45,510 --> 00:20:47,550
I was once a noble lady in Biantang.

317
00:20:48,000 --> 00:20:49,000
Twenty years ago,

318
00:20:49,680 --> 00:20:52,440
my father was involved
in the succession struggle

319
00:20:52,440 --> 00:20:54,270
between the current emperor
and his eldest brother,

320
00:20:54,270 --> 00:20:55,600
Crown Prince Maocheng.

321
00:20:56,590 --> 00:20:57,810
He was eventually implicated,

322
00:20:57,810 --> 00:21:00,170
and all my family members were executed.

323
00:21:01,790 --> 00:21:03,270
I was sold as a slave.

324
00:21:04,510 --> 00:21:06,480
Rou went through the same thing as I did.

325
00:21:06,480 --> 00:21:08,440
She also became a slave because of

326
00:21:08,640 --> 00:21:10,370
the palace coup at Xuri Palace.

327
00:21:10,800 --> 00:21:12,750
That's when we met.

328
00:21:16,510 --> 00:21:17,480
At first,

329
00:21:19,000 --> 00:21:19,880
Rou and I

330
00:21:19,880 --> 00:21:21,680
were sold to a brothel as slaves.

331
00:21:22,070 --> 00:21:24,000
We only did the lowest kind of work,

332
00:21:24,510 --> 00:21:25,930
didn't have enough to eat,

333
00:21:25,930 --> 00:21:28,510
and we weren't even allowed
to serve customers.

334
00:21:28,510 --> 00:21:30,440
In order to keep us alive,

335
00:21:31,330 --> 00:21:32,250
I stole

336
00:21:33,000 --> 00:21:34,370
and was beaten.

337
00:21:35,510 --> 00:21:36,240
Later,

338
00:21:37,000 --> 00:21:38,730
a customer took a liking to Rou,

339
00:21:39,480 --> 00:21:42,010
which is how
she entered a theater to perform.

340
00:21:46,440 --> 00:21:47,110
And I

341
00:21:47,880 --> 00:21:48,700
did everything I could,

342
00:21:48,700 --> 00:21:51,560
became a high-ranking servant
who could serve tea,

343
00:21:51,880 --> 00:21:55,000
and was eventually bought and sent
into the Crown Prince's Mansion,

344
00:21:55,000 --> 00:21:56,720
where I gained the Crown Prince's favor.

345
00:21:56,720 --> 00:21:59,720
Over the years,
I've been using my looks to please men,

346
00:22:00,920 --> 00:22:02,110
just to earn enough

347
00:22:02,110 --> 00:22:04,110
to keep Rou and me alive.

348
00:22:04,800 --> 00:22:06,350
The handkerchief you bought

349
00:22:06,350 --> 00:22:08,660
is how Rou and I secretly communicate.

350
00:22:09,510 --> 00:22:12,200
The code hidden in the stitches
is a form of women's script

351
00:22:12,200 --> 00:22:13,440
that Rou and I use

352
00:22:13,440 --> 00:22:15,500
to convey our feelings to each other.

353
00:22:16,750 --> 00:22:18,410
And the package I just gave her

354
00:22:20,440 --> 00:22:21,160
contained jewelry I secretly took

355
00:22:21,160 --> 00:22:23,200
from the Crown Prince's Mansion

356
00:22:23,730 --> 00:22:24,900
to support her.

357
00:22:25,000 --> 00:22:26,160
Does Li Ce know

358
00:22:27,240 --> 00:22:28,510
all of this?

359
00:22:28,510 --> 00:22:31,310
Your Highness,
I have no intention of harming him.

360
00:22:31,400 --> 00:22:32,890
His Highness is a good man.

361
00:22:32,910 --> 00:22:35,110
I will do my best to serve him.

362
00:22:35,640 --> 00:22:36,720
But if our backgrounds

363
00:22:36,720 --> 00:22:37,920
are ever discovered,

364
00:22:41,030 --> 00:22:44,360
I'm afraid even His Highness
wouldn't be able to protect us.

365
00:22:55,720 --> 00:22:57,780
You've been following me all the way.

366
00:23:06,270 --> 00:23:08,920
Why did you go and see
the Crown Prince of Biantang?

367
00:23:08,920 --> 00:23:09,670
I need him.

368
00:23:09,700 --> 00:23:11,560
What can someone like him even do?

369
00:23:12,390 --> 00:23:14,070
I've looked into Director Zhang.

370
00:23:14,070 --> 00:23:15,310
He is extremely cautious

371
00:23:15,310 --> 00:23:17,650
and has more than one residence
here in Tangjing,

372
00:23:17,650 --> 00:23:19,120
and his whereabouts are highly secret.

373
00:23:19,120 --> 00:23:21,450
He is not greedy for money, women,
or fame.

374
00:23:21,480 --> 00:23:22,790
He either stays indoors all day

375
00:23:22,790 --> 00:23:24,450
or is always heavily guarded.

376
00:23:24,590 --> 00:23:25,640
To find him,

377
00:23:25,830 --> 00:23:27,440
I need someone in Biantang

378
00:23:27,440 --> 00:23:28,750
who can move around freely.

379
00:23:28,750 --> 00:23:29,830
So you told him

380
00:23:29,830 --> 00:23:30,830
everything?

381
00:23:33,840 --> 00:23:35,300
How dare you ruin our plan?

382
00:23:41,830 --> 00:23:43,510
Don't resort to violence so easily.

383
00:23:43,510 --> 00:23:44,160
Also,

384
00:23:44,620 --> 00:23:45,900
don't follow me again.

385
00:23:51,370 --> 00:23:54,380
[Fuhe Pavilion]

386
00:24:06,310 --> 00:24:06,920
Qiao,

387
00:24:07,020 --> 00:24:07,930
you came just in time.

388
00:24:07,930 --> 00:24:09,140
I encountered something yesterday.

389
00:24:09,140 --> 00:24:10,350
-I want to discuss it with you.
-Li Ce.

390
00:24:10,350 --> 00:24:12,070
I also have something to discuss with you.

391
00:24:12,070 --> 00:24:13,590
It's about Lady Ziming.

392
00:24:13,830 --> 00:24:14,550
Ziming?

393
00:24:14,810 --> 00:24:15,720
What happened to her?

394
00:24:15,720 --> 00:24:17,380
Lady Ziming has a close friend

395
00:24:17,480 --> 00:24:18,200
named Rou.

396
00:24:18,880 --> 00:24:19,810
Do you know that?

397
00:24:23,690 --> 00:24:24,940
Here, enjoy.

398
00:24:25,200 --> 00:24:26,400
If it's the head, I'll send her away;

399
00:24:26,400 --> 00:24:27,840
if it's the tail, I won't.

400
00:24:31,660 --> 00:24:33,590
That doesn't count. One more time.

401
00:24:34,790 --> 00:24:37,720
You said yesterday
you would go back and think about it.

402
00:24:37,720 --> 00:24:38,780
How's the thinking going?

403
00:24:38,780 --> 00:24:39,640
Thinking what?

404
00:24:43,480 --> 00:24:44,160
I forgot.

405
00:24:44,640 --> 00:24:46,550
I had a more important thing
to think about yesterday,

406
00:24:46,550 --> 00:24:47,880
so I had no time for that.

407
00:24:48,950 --> 00:24:49,690
What was it?

408
00:24:49,720 --> 00:24:50,700
Since it's important,

409
00:24:50,700 --> 00:24:53,230
I naturally can't tell just anyone
so easily.

410
00:24:59,720 --> 00:25:01,350
Well, Zhuge Yue.

411
00:25:02,050 --> 00:25:04,180
we've known each other for a while now.

412
00:25:04,240 --> 00:25:06,000
We can be considered good brothers.

413
00:25:06,000 --> 00:25:07,400
Let me ask you something.

414
00:25:07,480 --> 00:25:09,080
You must answer truthfully.

415
00:25:09,190 --> 00:25:11,120
What do you think of me?

416
00:25:16,680 --> 00:25:17,310
Wait.

417
00:25:18,350 --> 00:25:21,350
I'm handsome, suave,

418
00:25:21,500 --> 00:25:23,240
elegant, and talented—

419
00:25:23,240 --> 00:25:25,700
there's no need
to mention those qualities.

420
00:25:27,550 --> 00:25:28,720
I mean,

421
00:25:28,720 --> 00:25:29,750
do I have any

422
00:25:29,750 --> 00:25:30,920
imperfections?

423
00:25:31,470 --> 00:25:32,330
For example...

424
00:25:32,350 --> 00:25:33,460
You talk too much.

425
00:25:34,310 --> 00:25:35,400
I talk too much?

426
00:25:35,880 --> 00:25:36,630
Then I'll stop talking.

427
00:25:36,630 --> 00:25:37,220
Wait!

428
00:25:39,960 --> 00:25:41,690
Why are we eating wontons here?

429
00:25:52,530 --> 00:25:53,250
Here you go.

430
00:26:03,080 --> 00:26:04,040
See that man?

431
00:26:05,270 --> 00:26:07,400
He should be Director Zhang's butler.

432
00:26:08,960 --> 00:26:11,640
Director Zhang
has more than one hidden residence.

433
00:26:11,640 --> 00:26:13,880
A few days ago, I sneaked into one of
his secret residences in the north of the city.

434
00:26:13,880 --> 00:26:14,880
I didn't find him,

435
00:26:15,110 --> 00:26:16,400
but I found some clues

436
00:26:16,720 --> 00:26:18,960
linked to this wonton stall.

437
00:26:20,480 --> 00:26:21,720
If I'm not mistaken,

438
00:26:22,200 --> 00:26:24,800
his second secret residence
should be nearby.

439
00:26:24,850 --> 00:26:27,570
The wontons
were bought for him by his butler.

440
00:26:37,610 --> 00:26:39,410
You came to see me for something?

441
00:26:47,720 --> 00:26:48,440
What is it?

442
00:26:52,070 --> 00:26:52,790
This matter

443
00:26:53,520 --> 00:26:54,680
is quite serious.

444
00:26:55,110 --> 00:26:56,310
Then say it quickly.

445
00:26:56,450 --> 00:26:57,140
It's...

446
00:26:58,510 --> 00:26:59,960
hard to explain in a few words.

447
00:26:59,960 --> 00:27:01,910
Then tell me once you've figured out
how to explain it.

448
00:27:01,910 --> 00:27:03,060
Qiao, don't go.

449
00:27:03,080 --> 00:27:04,810
Don't be so impatient. Come on.

450
00:27:05,030 --> 00:27:05,830
I'll tell you.

451
00:27:08,100 --> 00:27:09,210
In short,

452
00:27:09,240 --> 00:27:11,300
Ximeng has a lot of gold underground,

453
00:27:11,320 --> 00:27:13,150
but they can't mine it, so they're getting
anxious but can't do anything about it.

454
00:27:13,150 --> 00:27:14,790
Zhuge Yue came to me
to propose a cooperation.

455
00:27:14,790 --> 00:27:16,720
He asked me to help him find Director Zhang
from the Ministry of Works

456
00:27:16,720 --> 00:27:17,880
and his manufacturing diagram,

457
00:27:17,880 --> 00:27:19,310
and he promised me

458
00:27:19,590 --> 00:27:21,240
one-tenth of the profits afterward.

459
00:27:21,240 --> 00:27:21,790
No,

460
00:27:22,590 --> 00:27:23,550
two-tenths.

461
00:27:23,790 --> 00:27:25,240
What are you talking about?

462
00:27:25,240 --> 00:27:26,700
Princess, Your Highness.

463
00:27:26,790 --> 00:27:28,450
Ziming requests an audience.

464
00:27:33,710 --> 00:27:35,030
I'm sorry, Your Highness.

465
00:27:35,030 --> 00:27:36,560
Dear, what are you doing?

466
00:27:37,000 --> 00:27:38,720
I've been concealing something
from you, Your Highness,

467
00:27:38,720 --> 00:27:40,180
and I feel guilty about it.

468
00:27:41,330 --> 00:27:43,520
Although I have failed your favor,

469
00:27:43,640 --> 00:27:44,740
I beg you, Your Highness,

470
00:27:44,740 --> 00:27:46,240
for the sake of the child in my womb,

471
00:27:46,240 --> 00:27:47,310
do not send me away.

472
00:27:48,880 --> 00:27:51,110
I am pregnant with your child.

473
00:27:51,330 --> 00:27:52,140
Child?

474
00:28:03,030 --> 00:28:04,890
Congratulations, Elder Helian.

475
00:28:05,070 --> 00:28:06,510
The day before yesterday, His Majesty

476
00:28:06,510 --> 00:28:08,540
announced the news
of making Lady Helian his concubine

477
00:28:08,540 --> 00:28:09,490
to the world.

478
00:28:10,680 --> 00:28:12,440
This has finally put us tribe elders

479
00:28:12,440 --> 00:28:13,510
of Great Yan

480
00:28:14,160 --> 00:28:15,240
at ease.

481
00:28:15,480 --> 00:28:17,830
The future of Great Yan is now secured.

482
00:28:20,750 --> 00:28:23,310
I always thought His Majesty
was reluctant to take a queen

483
00:28:23,310 --> 00:28:25,840
because he still had feelings
for that slave.

484
00:28:26,050 --> 00:28:28,690
Even the niece I sent to him

485
00:28:28,710 --> 00:28:30,640
was sent back without hesitation.

486
00:28:31,240 --> 00:28:33,440
I didn't expect that Helian Tribe,

487
00:28:34,350 --> 00:28:36,280
though poor at riding and warfare,

488
00:28:37,350 --> 00:28:38,480
to be so clever

489
00:28:39,830 --> 00:28:41,880
when it comes to offering women.

490
00:28:44,110 --> 00:28:47,070
Elder Pale, you must be joking.

491
00:28:49,640 --> 00:28:50,240
Enough of this.

492
00:28:50,240 --> 00:28:51,830
Come, come, let's drink.

493
00:28:52,310 --> 00:28:53,070
Come on.

494
00:28:54,090 --> 00:28:55,570
Come on, let's drink.

495
00:28:57,960 --> 00:28:58,750
Good wine.

496
00:28:59,240 --> 00:28:59,880
Elders,

497
00:28:59,880 --> 00:29:02,410
since you are here to congratulate me
on becoming the Queen,

498
00:29:02,410 --> 00:29:04,960
why did you start the banquet
without me?

499
00:29:05,590 --> 00:29:06,550
Why are you here?

500
00:29:06,760 --> 00:29:07,890
If I hadn't come,

501
00:29:08,080 --> 00:29:10,110
how would I know
who are the Helian Tribe's friends

502
00:29:10,110 --> 00:29:11,750
and who are our enemies?

503
00:29:12,510 --> 00:29:14,320
And how could I speak well of you

504
00:29:14,350 --> 00:29:16,020
before His Majesty?

505
00:29:18,280 --> 00:29:21,440
The Helian Tribe
has truly become something.

506
00:29:22,480 --> 00:29:25,440
We'll have to be more careful
with our words in the future.

507
00:29:25,440 --> 00:29:28,590
Although the Helian Tribe has no troops,

508
00:29:29,640 --> 00:29:31,320
it has women.

509
00:29:33,920 --> 00:29:35,380
Elder Pale, you're right.

510
00:29:36,160 --> 00:29:38,070
I used to think

511
00:29:38,070 --> 00:29:40,200
only troops could strengthen a tribe.

512
00:29:40,680 --> 00:29:42,790
But now I finally realize

513
00:29:43,680 --> 00:29:44,680
that sometimes,

514
00:29:45,310 --> 00:29:47,960
women can be very different
from each other.

515
00:29:48,640 --> 00:29:50,440
If a woman is a princess consort,

516
00:29:50,750 --> 00:29:53,280
she can be more valuable
than thousands of men

517
00:29:53,280 --> 00:29:55,890
and thousands of fine cavalry.

518
00:29:55,920 --> 00:29:56,480
You...

519
00:29:57,880 --> 00:29:59,830
Princess Consort Helian,
you're absolutely right.

520
00:29:59,830 --> 00:30:01,310
Although His Majesty
is wise and formidable,

521
00:30:01,310 --> 00:30:02,640
he is also inscrutable.

522
00:30:02,920 --> 00:30:03,960
We have long been troubled by the fact

523
00:30:03,960 --> 00:30:05,960
that he has no one truly close to him.

524
00:30:06,030 --> 00:30:07,160
Now that we have you,

525
00:30:07,440 --> 00:30:10,570
we hope you will look after us,
Princess Consort Helian.

526
00:30:13,480 --> 00:30:14,410
You're too kind.

527
00:30:15,790 --> 00:30:17,830
Although His Majesty favors me now,

528
00:30:17,830 --> 00:30:20,030
the Helian Tribe is still weak.

529
00:30:20,400 --> 00:30:22,720
I will still need your support.

530
00:30:23,510 --> 00:30:24,550
You flatter us.

531
00:30:24,830 --> 00:30:26,440
You've just been named Princess Consort.

532
00:30:26,440 --> 00:30:28,270
You must have a lot of things
to deal with.

533
00:30:28,270 --> 00:30:29,730
We will take our leave now.

534
00:30:29,920 --> 00:30:30,510
Let's go.

535
00:30:30,750 --> 00:30:31,560
Farewell.

536
00:30:32,570 --> 00:30:33,160
Let's go.

537
00:30:34,810 --> 00:30:35,400
Let's go!

538
00:30:46,880 --> 00:30:48,740
I am the chief of the Helian Tribe.

539
00:30:49,230 --> 00:30:51,960
Who allowed you to come here
and tell me what to do?

540
00:30:58,590 --> 00:30:59,480
Helian Chuan,

541
00:31:00,240 --> 00:31:01,330
listen carefully.

542
00:31:02,480 --> 00:31:05,790
From now on, you are
the head of the family in name only.

543
00:31:06,400 --> 00:31:07,440
In reality,

544
00:31:08,350 --> 00:31:10,480
I am the Princess Consort of Great Yan.

545
00:31:10,750 --> 00:31:12,160
You must always remember

546
00:31:13,110 --> 00:31:14,070
that without me,

547
00:31:16,680 --> 00:31:17,680
you are nothing but a coward

548
00:31:17,680 --> 00:31:19,550
who sold your sister's body

549
00:31:19,550 --> 00:31:22,960
for a few worthless horses.

550
00:31:28,450 --> 00:31:29,050
Do it!

551
00:31:29,960 --> 00:31:31,000
Kill me!

552
00:31:31,230 --> 00:31:33,400
Then send my body to Yan Xun.

553
00:31:40,160 --> 00:31:41,160
You loser.

554
00:32:01,370 --> 00:32:02,880
Yesterday,
I wrote a letter to Director Zhang

555
00:32:02,880 --> 00:32:04,270
in your name.

556
00:32:06,960 --> 00:32:08,440
I bribed the stall owner
to put it in the food box,

557
00:32:08,440 --> 00:32:09,920
and the butler has already taken it.

558
00:32:09,920 --> 00:32:11,270
Let's wait here for a while.

559
00:32:11,270 --> 00:32:12,360
Let's see if he's willing to come out

560
00:32:12,360 --> 00:32:14,080
and meet us after he reads it.

561
00:32:14,160 --> 00:32:15,510
Why did you use my name?

562
00:32:16,410 --> 00:32:17,170
Be quiet.

563
00:32:38,640 --> 00:32:39,790
Don't look for me.

564
00:32:40,240 --> 00:32:41,840
The wontons have gone mushy.

565
00:32:42,200 --> 00:32:43,680
Your method didn't work.

566
00:32:48,940 --> 00:32:50,070
Something's wrong.

567
00:32:50,330 --> 00:32:51,500
This is Xing's handwriting.

568
00:32:51,500 --> 00:32:52,500
Stop looking.

569
00:32:52,830 --> 00:32:54,640
Director Zhang is no longer here.

570
00:32:54,640 --> 00:32:56,830
The Ministry of Works decided to build
a river channel yesterday.

571
00:32:56,830 --> 00:32:59,070
He has moved to
the Manufacturing Bureau overnight.

572
00:32:59,070 --> 00:33:00,330
If you want to find him,

573
00:33:00,400 --> 00:33:01,350
I can help you.

574
00:33:01,880 --> 00:33:04,340
But we want
an additional 10 percent profit.

575
00:33:07,850 --> 00:33:08,770
This is risky.

576
00:33:08,800 --> 00:33:09,930
I'm not helping you.

577
00:33:10,860 --> 00:33:11,900
I'm helping Li Ce.

578
00:33:13,400 --> 00:33:13,990
Besides,

579
00:33:14,920 --> 00:33:17,320
I have the map
of the Manufacturing Bureau.

580
00:33:25,440 --> 00:33:26,030
Qiao,

581
00:33:26,720 --> 00:33:28,780
this is the outfit I specially bought

582
00:33:29,890 --> 00:33:31,350
for tonight's operation.

583
00:33:31,440 --> 00:33:33,960
Am I breathtakingly handsome

584
00:33:34,160 --> 00:33:36,070
and unrivaled in the world?

585
00:33:36,550 --> 00:33:38,480
Something like breaking into
the Manufacturing Bureau at night—

586
00:33:38,480 --> 00:33:40,340
Zhuge Yue can handle it on his own.

587
00:33:40,550 --> 00:33:42,150
You don't know martial arts.

588
00:33:42,530 --> 00:33:43,290
If you go...

589
00:33:43,310 --> 00:33:43,940
Qiao,

590
00:33:44,350 --> 00:33:45,400
don't worry.

591
00:33:45,960 --> 00:33:47,590
It's inconvenient
for Zhuge Yue to show up.

592
00:33:47,590 --> 00:33:49,410
I must use my identity as the Crown Prince

593
00:33:49,410 --> 00:33:51,410
to persuade Director Zhang to help.

594
00:33:52,000 --> 00:33:52,800
Rest assured.

595
00:33:53,110 --> 00:33:54,480
I've memorized the map
of the Manufacturing Bureau

596
00:33:54,480 --> 00:33:55,680
drawn by Wang Shi'er.

597
00:33:55,880 --> 00:33:58,160
Zhuge Yue will be fine with me.

598
00:33:58,510 --> 00:33:59,240
Li Ce,

599
00:34:00,030 --> 00:34:02,350
actually, you don't have to cooperate
with Zhuge Yue.

600
00:34:02,350 --> 00:34:03,610
According to our plan,

601
00:34:03,720 --> 00:34:05,320
we can build up our own power.

602
00:34:05,680 --> 00:34:07,660
We don't need his 30 percent share
of the gold mine

603
00:34:07,660 --> 00:34:10,120
to expand our power
and counter the Empress.

604
00:34:13,840 --> 00:34:14,480
Qiao.

605
00:34:16,070 --> 00:34:18,440
I said I'd take you back to Biantang
to recover,

606
00:34:18,440 --> 00:34:20,170
but since you came back with me,

607
00:34:20,880 --> 00:34:23,010
you've been living in constant danger

608
00:34:23,340 --> 00:34:25,070
without a single peaceful day.

609
00:34:26,199 --> 00:34:28,330
I've played the fool for so many years.

610
00:34:29,110 --> 00:34:31,370
I said I wanted to regroup and start over,

611
00:34:32,230 --> 00:34:33,070
but in the end,

612
00:34:34,840 --> 00:34:37,699
I still have to rely on you
to fight my battles for me.

613
00:34:37,920 --> 00:34:40,670
I feel very bad about it.

614
00:34:46,150 --> 00:34:46,710
However,

615
00:34:47,070 --> 00:34:47,880
I have always been a good man

616
00:34:47,880 --> 00:34:49,610
who repays evil with kindness.

617
00:34:50,630 --> 00:34:52,750
So you've always had someone else
in your heart

618
00:34:52,750 --> 00:34:54,270
and treated me roughly,

619
00:34:55,030 --> 00:34:56,290
but it doesn't matter.

620
00:34:56,580 --> 00:34:58,510
I've already left a way out for you.

621
00:34:58,520 --> 00:35:00,080
Inside here are over 50

622
00:35:00,100 --> 00:35:02,360
shop deeds from various cities
across Biantang and Great Yong,

623
00:35:02,360 --> 00:35:03,910
along with thousands of mu
of fertile farmland.

624
00:35:03,910 --> 00:35:05,910
If anything happens to me this time,

625
00:35:06,270 --> 00:35:07,710
go to the pawnshop, get the money,

626
00:35:07,710 --> 00:35:08,840
and leave Biantang.

627
00:35:18,460 --> 00:35:20,260
You're getting physical again!

628
00:35:21,230 --> 00:35:22,140
Jinx.

629
00:35:39,080 --> 00:35:40,030
Strange.

630
00:35:44,340 --> 00:35:46,700
Where is that

631
00:35:48,220 --> 00:35:49,480
"Water Conservancy"?

632
00:36:00,670 --> 00:36:02,030
Who are you?

633
00:36:04,430 --> 00:36:05,290
Your Highness.

634
00:36:08,150 --> 00:36:10,210
It's not your first day working here.

635
00:36:10,440 --> 00:36:12,680
Don't you know the Crown Prince wants
Honghe fish?

636
00:36:12,680 --> 00:36:14,070
Of course I know.

637
00:36:14,840 --> 00:36:17,000
But Honghe fish is rare

638
00:36:17,400 --> 00:36:19,200
and only sold in the West Market.

639
00:36:19,360 --> 00:36:21,840
I usually go early in the morning

640
00:36:21,910 --> 00:36:23,670
to get the fresh ones.

641
00:36:23,920 --> 00:36:27,150
But unfortunately,
I was a quarter of an hour late today.

642
00:36:27,880 --> 00:36:29,440
The best Honghe fish

643
00:36:29,700 --> 00:36:31,380
was sent to the Zhan's Manor.

644
00:36:32,010 --> 00:36:32,950
Honghe fish?

645
00:36:33,460 --> 00:36:34,060
Sister,

646
00:36:34,210 --> 00:36:35,370
this is Honghe fish.

647
00:36:35,480 --> 00:36:36,400
It's very rare.

648
00:36:41,450 --> 00:36:42,100
Your Highness.

649
00:36:42,100 --> 00:36:42,960
Your Highness.

650
00:36:43,190 --> 00:36:44,030
Are you saying

651
00:36:44,160 --> 00:36:46,020
Lord Zhan also likes Honghe fish?

652
00:36:46,710 --> 00:36:47,840
Yes, Your Highness.

653
00:36:48,720 --> 00:36:51,850
It's said that, apart from me,
the only regular customer

654
00:36:51,930 --> 00:36:53,880
of the shop selling Honghe fish
in the West Market

655
00:36:53,880 --> 00:36:55,550
is Zhan's Mansion.

656
00:37:12,430 --> 00:37:13,070
Princess Fu.

657
00:37:13,070 --> 00:37:14,070
Where is your lady?

658
00:37:14,070 --> 00:37:14,710
Our lady?

659
00:37:17,630 --> 00:37:18,920
She was sleeping here

660
00:37:18,920 --> 00:37:19,960
just an hour ago.

661
00:37:20,930 --> 00:37:22,290
Where did she go?

662
00:37:27,740 --> 00:37:28,340
Take care.

663
00:37:31,280 --> 00:37:31,960
Ziming...

664
00:37:32,800 --> 00:37:34,060
works for the Empress!

665
00:37:35,180 --> 00:37:38,070
[One day ago]

666
00:38:19,630 --> 00:38:20,430
Catch them!

667
00:38:22,670 --> 00:38:24,480
Your Majesty, are you feeling guilty

668
00:38:24,480 --> 00:38:25,750
that you don't dare to see me?

669
00:38:25,750 --> 00:38:27,090
If you can't get rid of him,

670
00:38:27,090 --> 00:38:28,520
you are nothing but useless trash.

671
00:38:28,520 --> 00:38:30,050
Get out! Get out, all of you!

672
00:38:30,060 --> 00:38:32,690
If you like me, marry me
and make me your princess consort.

673
00:38:32,690 --> 00:38:36,290
And bring a moment of peace
to the millions of people in Great Yan!

674
00:38:36,370 --> 00:38:37,570
There are some things

675
00:38:37,980 --> 00:38:39,100
I must do.

